{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ab0da0af9b","title":"给陈公培的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c62fc71adf","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":4,"articleId":"ab0da0af9b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5feb93f34f","type":"paragraph","text":"给陈公培的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"ab0da0af9b"},{"id":"9c0d621cef","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年11月4日）公培兄大鉴：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"ab0da0af9b"},{"id":"d72d601a9b","type":"paragraph","text":"又数年不见了，得悉吾兄依然奋斗不解，同人闻之十分佩感相距尚远，不能聚首，望用书面时通消息。各方统一战线，深仗大力轻旋，对内则化干戈为玉帛，对外则求一致之抗战，争取民族革命战争与民主共和国之联系及其彻底胜利之前途。疾风劲草，愿共努力！顺祝行止佳胜！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"ab0da0af9b"},{"id":"974b9f6533","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"ab0da0af9b"},{"id":"1afb13c8c1","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月四号","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"ab0da0af9b"},{"id":"2dee9f0edf","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]陈公培（1901-1968），湖南长沙人。早年参加过中国共产党。1933年福建人民革命政府时期，他是十九路军与红军联络的代表。新中国成立后，曾任政务院参事。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"ab0da0af9b"}],"page":{"id":"2702d36c27","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"ab0da0af9b","start":278,"end":278}}}},"__N_SSG":true}